title: EP 144: GETTING OUT OF DYSFUNCTION AND INTO FULFILLING YOUR DREAMS
description: This episode I get super deep on removing yourself from dysfunctional family dynamics. What goes into getting out and how do we maintain those boundaries? An emailer writes in about her Narcissistic dad trying to get back into her life. What should she do? A young lady writes in about having trouble getting motivated. She has the dream, but how to get into DOING? How does she get over the low self esteem that is  holding her back? Let's get our lives and get super deep on this one, bros!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
